==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Grumous
<hw>Gru"mous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>grumeleux</ets>. See <er>Grume</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Resembling or containing grume; thick; concreted; clotted; <as>as,
grumous blood</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>See <er>Grumose</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Grumousness</ent>⟦br⟧
